beer.beer_description: Monkey's Uncle Red Ale is brewed using the finest barley, hops and water from our spring in Clare, South Australia. Extended kilning of the red malts give this beer its striking complexion and intriguing, if slightly nutty, appeal. This lively ale, has caramel and biscuity flavours amongst the mid-palate of toffee apple and treacle. Enjoy the great taste of Monkey's Uncle Red Ale... Well I'll be a monkey's uncle - this red ale is damn good!!
